        "content": "**Log browsing is deferred to the ClickHouse / HyperDX analytics stack** (MOQT-native log streaming + OTEL).\n\nUntil then:\n- live relay log: `ssh moqx-ci` \u2192 `docker logs -f moqx`, or the Dozzle `logmon` container (`127.0.0.1:9999` on the box)\n- kernel events: `dmesg -T | tail`\n\nThe Kernel UDP health panel (left) covers the platform signal that matters most for a QUIC relay: kernel-level datagram drops.",
